des:
Group Therapy is a skill that gives you ideas to write about in group therapy sessions or just for fun and games. All of the ideas come from people from all over the country. You can get over 30 different ideas to use in your own behavioral counseling group activities. Use this skill to help you better conduct group therapy sessions or to have fun. 

You can even submit your own ideas to be used in this skill. 

Disclaimer - The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment, or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number
